description: Semantic Tags include meta, head, header, section, article, aside, footer, etc. btw This page looks like the front page of the blog.
This tutorial also covers a little CSS. Attach id to tags and use &ltstyle&gt #main-header{} to change bgcolor, textcolor, size, padding etc. Will further studying it in later tutorials.




